title: Her Mannequin
description: A walking, talking mannequin. Is this an opportunity to use, or an opportunity to be used? Bora simply wants a chance to get close to the fashion designer, Hongrin Da. Yet it would seem that Hongrin wants something more from Bora. Will Bora’s struggles to become a fashion designer pull at Hongrin’s heartstrings? If she even has any to begin with...
